    <item>
      <title>德意志银行四年来首次亏损后放弃回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/deutsche-bank-suffers-first-loss-in-four-years-on-legacy-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行表示，在遭遇四年来首次季度亏损后，该银行今年很可能不会进行第二次股票回购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/deutsche-bank-suffers-first-loss-in-four-years-on-legacy-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:04:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桑坦德银行提高收入目标，博廷银行效率提高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/santander-posts-record-profit-as-it-beat-quarterly-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[桑坦德银行上调了今年的收入增长目标，并表示在第二季度创下创纪录的利润后，将继续致力于控制成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/santander-posts-record-profit-as-it-beat-quarterly-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:02:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政策希望消退 中国股市遭遇 1 月以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/chinese-stocks-trim-losses-amid-signs-national-team-in-action</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市以今年早些时候大跌以来未曾见过的速度下跌，再次引发人们对尽管实施了政策缓冲，但市场仍将再次陷入自由落体式下跌的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/chinese-stocks-trim-losses-amid-signs-national-team-in-action</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 04:31:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉和 LVMH 业绩令人失望，股市暴跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司、路易威登集团和德意志银行公布的业绩不佳导致股市暴跌，随着财报季进入高潮，人们开始担心全球商业状况。纳斯达克 100 指数期货早盘下跌近 1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 23:18:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
